        <div class="observation__author">Joe Turner</div>
        <div class="observation__description">
          <p>No snow, driving on a snowmachine from Kaltag to Unalakleet. Creeks running open with open water. Low snow and warm temps meant the snowmachine kept overheating, and I had to make many stops.  This change affects hunting and village travel.  I first started noticing this change in 2013.  I observe this change seasonally. It has a strong effect on safety.</p>
        </div>
